    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>As a reaction, a witchwyrd can use any number of its free hands to catch @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.jUTs9R52bL7SuHwY]{Magic Missile} (from the spell of the same name) fired at it. Doing so absorbs the missile and manifests as a glowing nimbus around that hand (which is no longer considered free). The energy lasts 6 rounds or until it is used to create an additional @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.1DHUPmtu6gKUKc0a]{Force Bolt} (see below). To use this ability, the witchwyrd must be aware of the incoming magic missile and cannot be @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Flat-footed}.</p>"
